{"word":"θυρώματα","slug":"θυρώματα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θυρώματα</b></el> <el>(θύρωματα, τά,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θυρόω'><el>θυρόω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a room with doors to it, a chamber</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a door with posts and frame</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}